<!-- Company Story Section -->
<section class="story-section py-5" aria-labelledby="story-title">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <div class="text-center mb-5">
                    <h2 id="story-title" class="display-5 fw-bold mb-3">Our Story</h2>
                    <p class="lead text-secondary">
                        Founded by healthcare professionals and technology experts who saw the need 
                        for better coordination in transplant care.
                    </p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="story-content">
                    <div class="modern-card p-4 mb-4">
                        <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">The Challenge</h4>
                        <p class="text-secondary mb-0">
                            Transplant care involves complex coordination between multiple stakeholders - patients, 
                            dialysis units, transplant centers, and care teams. Traditional communication methods 
                            often lead to delays, miscommunication, and suboptimal patient outcomes. We recognized 
                            the urgent need for a unified, secure platform that could streamline these critical interactions.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="modern-card p-4 mb-4">
                        <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Our Solution</h4>
                        <p class="text-secondary mb-0">
                            TransplantWizard was born from the vision of creating a comprehensive platform that 
                            connects all aspects of transplant care. Our HIPAA-compliant solution provides dedicated 
                            portals for each stakeholder while maintaining seamless data flow and communication. 
                            We've built enterprise-grade security into every aspect of our platform to ensure 
                            patient data remains protected.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="modern-card p-4">
                        <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Our Impact</h4>
                        <p class="text-secondary mb-0">
                            Since our launch, we've facilitated thousands of patient referrals, improved coordination 
                            for hundreds of healthcare organizations, and most importantly, contributed to better 
                            patient outcomes across the transplant care continuum. Our platform continues to evolve 
                            based on feedback from the healthcare professionals who use it every day.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

